# Admin allowlist
# Server-only. Comma-separated list of admin emails.
# Case-insensitive + whitespace-trimmed exact-string match.
# Plus-addressed variants are NOT normalized (e.g., admin+ops@x.com is distinct from admin@x.com).
# Example: ADMIN_EMAILS=admin1@example.com,admin2@example.com
ADMIN_EMAILS=
